ck_confirm_msg:"Scores will be recomputed from current points. The match returns to read-only after closing.",match_relock_confirm_label:"Close again",delete_match:"Delete match?",delete_matchup:"Delete matchup?",delete_matchup_msg:"All scouted points in this matchup will be permanently lost.",delete_player:"Delete player?",delete_team:"Delete team?",delete_layout:"Delete layout?",delete_tactic:"Delete tactic?",empty_no_data:"No data yet",empty_add_matches:"Add matches to see stats",empty_no_players:"No players in this squad",empty_no_squads:"Form at least 2 squads to start matchups",insight_fifty_text:e=>`Aggressive fifty — reached in ${e}% of points`,insight_fifty_detail_named:e=>`Most often via ${e}. League average is ~35%.`,insight_fifty_detail_nameless:"League average is around 35%.",insight_pocket_text:e=>`Heavy pocket — ${e} players delay, shooting lanes`,insight_pocket_detail:"They shoot heavy break lanes. Priority: survive the start, don't run through paint.",insight_conservative_text:e=>`Slow tempo — ${e} runner${e===1?"":"s"} on the break`,insight_conservative_detail:"Slow pace. Get alive first, then build pressure from angles — the tape opens up.",insight_agg_start_text:e=>`Aggressive break — ${e} go on the buzzer`,insight_agg_start_detail:"They send many runners on break. Disciplined lanes will catch them in the open.",insight_dorito_dominant_text:e=>`Dorito-heavy — ${e}% of points`,insight_dorito_dominant_detail:"Their main side. Snake will be under-defended — send a player there.",insight_snake_dominant_text:e=>`Snake-heavy — ${e}% of points`,insight_snake_dominant_detail:"Their main side. Dorito will be under-defended — send a player there.",insight_side_vuln_text:(e,t)=>`Loses points when attacked through ${e} — ${t}% of losses`,insight_side_vuln_detail:e=>`We win ${e}% when we attack that side. Keep pressuring there.`,insight_center_text:e=>`Controls center in ${e}% of points`,insight_center_detail:"They dominate center — limit crossfires and respect the mid player.",insight_uncovered_text:e=>`They don't shoot toward ${e} during obstacle play`,insight_uncovered_detail:e=>`A player entering through ${e} will meet minimal resistance.`,insight_player_strong_text:e=>`Key player makes a big difference (+${e}% win rate when playing)`,insight_player_strong_detail:(e,t,n)=>`With them: ${e}% wins. Without: ${t}% (${n} pts).`,insight_player_weak_text:e=>`One player drags the team (${e}%)`,insight_player_weak_detail:(e,t,n)=>`With them: ${e}% wins vs ${t}% without (${n} pts).`,insight_late_break_text:e=>`Secondary push after break — ${e}% of points`,insight_late_break_detail:"They send a player a moment after the buzzer. Hold lanes active for a few seconds.",insight_predictable_text:e=>`Predictable — same setup in ${e}% of points`,insight_predictable_detail:(e,t,n)=>`${e} of ${t} points: ${n}. Prep a specific counter.`,insight_unpredictable_text:e=>`Unpredictable — ${e} different break setups`,insight_unpredictable_detail:e=>`No setup dominates (max ${e}%). Play solid fundamentals, not one counter.`,formation_on_dorito:e=>`${e} on dorito`,formation_on_snake:e=>`${e} on snake`,formation_in_center:e=>`${e} in center`,counter_fifty_action:e=>`Hold lanes on the ${e} side`,counter_fifty_detail:e=>`They push the fifty aggressively via ${e}. Set a player to hold the lane and kill the runner before they reach the fifty.`,counter_pocket_action:"Survive the break — read their lanes",counter_pocket_detail:"They have 4+ players shooting from the base. Don't run through paint — wait for a reload or quiet moment, then attack the open tape.",counter_conservative_action:"Get alive, then apply pressure",counter_conservative_detail:"They play slow. Get alive on good bunkers first, then build pressure from the angles. Don't force the break.",counter_agg_start_action:"Lanes on break — free eliminations",counter_agg_start_detail:"They send many runners. Disciplined lanes off the buzzer rack up eliminations before they reach their bunkers.",